        "text": "Psalm 57:5",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", cf. לטשׁ, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Psalm 7:13",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "). The excitement and indignant anger against one's foes which expresses itself in the rhythm and the choice of words, has been already recognised by us since ",
        "children": []
